description.p:
The nucleotide sequence and the amino acid sequence for the human S1P1/EDG1 receptor are known in the art and are published in e.g.: Hla, T., and Maciag, T. J. Biol Chem. 265 (1990), 9308-9313; WO 91/15583 published 17 October 1991; WO 99/46277 published 16 September 1999. The potency and efficacy of the compounds of formula (I) are assessed using a GTPγS assay to determine EC50 values and by measuring the circulating lymphocytes in the rat after oral administration, respectively (see in Examples).
